# Apps Script Project (clasp)

This repo is a **Google Apps Script** project managed locally with **clasp**. Follow these conventions.

## File structure

- **`.gs`** — Server-side code (Code.gs, Api.gs, etc.). Prefer `.gs` for all server-side logic.
- **`.html`** — HtmlService templates and fragments (e.g. Index.html, Style.html, JavaScript.html).
- **`appsscript.json`** — Manifest only. Do not add custom build or bundling config here.

Keep the standard Apps Script layout; do not rename to `.js` for server code unless required by an explicit request.

## Deployment

- **Deployment path**: `clasp push` (and `clasp deploy` when publishing).
- Do not introduce npm/webpack/vite/other build tooling unless the user explicitly asks for it.
- Assume the project runs in the Apps Script runtime; no Node/browser bundling.

## When editing

- Add or change server logic in `.gs` files.
- Add or change UI/templates in `.html` files.
- Respect `.claspignore` so only intended files are pushed (e.g. `*.gs`, `*.html`, `appsscript.json`).
